1. waitbus corpus generator code
--------------------------------
Files: `benchmarks/gen_corpus.py`, `scripts/derive_gh_distributions.py`,
       `benchmarks/data/corpus.jsonl.gz`, `benchmarks/data/gh_distributions.toml`.
